{"type":"assistant","uuid":"20260312040352e18a29c32a964d95","session_id":"da6f98d4-7e33-4c58-9c42-a371874e10ea","message":{"id":"20260312040352e18a29c32a964d95","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"019cde7faca8771a29615f017aeb0eea","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/005-pipeline-status-and-log-streaming/plan.md","content":"# F-005: Pipeline Status Aggregation and Log Streaming — Technical Plan\n\n## 1. Architecture Overview\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                         Telegram Command Router (F-002)                      │\n│                    src/bot/commands/handlers/status.js                       │\n│                    src/bot/commands/handlers/logs.js                          │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                                      │\n                                      ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                      Status Aggregator (NEW)                                 │\n│                    src/services/status-aggregator.js                         │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐    │\n│  │ • aggregateStatus()   • formatStatusForTelegram()                   │    │\n│  │ • calculateProgress() • getErrorSummary()                           │    │\n│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘    │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                                      │\n                                      ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                       Log Pager (NEW)                                        │\n│                    src/services/log-pager.js                                 │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐    │\n│  │ • readLogPage()       • formatLogsForTelegram()                     │    │\n│  │ • extractErrorLines() • shouldSendAsFile()                          │    │\n│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘    │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                                      │\n                                      ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    Telegram Pusher (NEW)                                     │\n│                    src/services/telegram-pusher.js                           │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐    │\n│  │ • pushHeartbeat()     • pushErrorSummary()                          │    │\n│  │ • sendMessageChunked() • throttle()                                 │    │\n│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘    │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                    │                      │\n                    ▼                      ▼\n┌─────────────────────────┐ ┌─────────────────────────┐\n│   State Manager (F-004) │ │  Pipeline Controller    │\n│    state-manager.js     │ │  pipeline-controller.js │\n├─────────────────────────┤ ├─────────────────────────┤\n│ • readDaemonMeta()      │ │ • getStatus()           │\n│ • readPipelineState()   │ │ • getLogs()             │\n│ • getLastResult()       │ │                         │\n└─────────────────────────┘ └─────────────────────────┘\n                    │                      │\n                    └──────────────────────┘\n                                           ▼\n                    ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n                    │                       State Files                       │\n                    │  state/pipeline.json, state/.pipeline-meta.json        │\n                    │  state/pipeline-daemon.log, state/.last-result.json    │\n                    │  bugfix-state/... (mirror structure)                    │\n                    └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## 2. Component Design\n\n### 2.1 Status Aggregator (`src/services/status-aggregator.js`)\n\n**职责**: 聚合多个状态源，生成结构化的状态报告\n\n**核心方法**:\n\n```javascript\nexport function createStatusAggregator(options = {}) {\n  const {\n    stateManager = getDefaultStateManager(),\n    pipelineController = getDefaultPipelineController(),\n    config = loadPipelineInfraConfig()\n  } = options;\n\n  return {\n    // Main aggregation\n    async aggregateStatus(type),\n\n    // Formatting\n    formatStatusForTelegram(status),\n\n    // Helpers\n    calculateProgress(state),\n    getErrorSummary(lastResult),\n    determinePipelineStage(state, daemonMeta),\n  };\n}\n```\n\n**状态聚合流程**:\n1. 读取 `pipeline.json` 获取运行状态\n2. 读取 `.pipeline-meta.json` 获取 daemon 信息\n3. 读取 `.last-result.json` 获取历史结果\n4. 读取 `current-session.json` 获取当前 feature\n5. 聚合生成统一的状态对象\n\n---\n\n### 2.2 Log Pager (`src/services/log-pager.js`)\n\n**职责**: 分页读取日志，支持偏移和行数限制\n\n**核心方法**:\n\n```javascript\nexport function createLogPager(options = {}) {\n  const {\n    stateManager = getDefaultStateManager(),\n    config = loadPipelineInfraConfig()\n  } = options;\n\n  return {\n    // Main reading\n    async readLogPage(type, options),\n\n    // Formatting\n    formatLogsForTelegram(logs, metadata),\n\n    // Helpers\n    extractErrorLines(logs, lineCount),\n    shouldSendAsFile(logs, thresholdBytes),\n    buildLogMetadata(logPath, totalLines, pageStart, pageEnd),\n  };\n}\n```\n\n**日志读取流程**:\n1. 解析分页参数 (lines, offset)\n2. 读取日志文件（流式读取大文件）\n3. 提取指定范围\n4. 生成格式化输出\n\n---\n\n### 2.3 Telegram Pusher (`src/services/telegram-pusher.js`)\n\n**职责**: 管理 Telegram 消息推送，包括心跳和错误摘要\n\n**核心方法**:\n\n```javascript\nexport function createTelegramPusher(options = {}) {\n  const {\n    bot,\n    targetChatId,\n    heartbeatInterval = 30 * 1000, // 30 seconds\n    errorLinesCount = 10,\n    throttleInterval = 30 * 1000,\n  } = options;\n\n  return {\n    // Heartbeat\n    startHeartbeat(type, aggregator),\n    stopHeartbeat(type),\n\n    // Error push\n    async pushErrorSummary(type, featureId, error),\n\n    // Message sending\n    async sendMessageChunked(chatId, text),\n    async sendFile(chatId, content, filename),\n\n    // Throttling\n    throttle(key, fn),\n  };\n}\n```\n\n**推送流程**:\n1. Pipeline 启动时调用 `startHeartbeat`\n2. 定时检查状态并推送进度\n3. 收到错误事件时调用 `pushErrorSummary`\n4. Pipeline 停止时调用 `stopHeartbeat`\n\n---\n\n### 2.4 Enhanced Status Handler (`src/bot/commands/handlers/status.js`)\n\n**增强现有处理器**:\n\n```javascript\nexport async function handleStatus(handlerCtx) {\n  const { reply, params } = handlerCtx;\n  const pipelineType = params.type || 'feature';\n\n  const aggregator = createStatusAggregator();\n  const status = await aggregator.aggregateStatus(pipelineType);\n  const formatted = aggregator.formatStatusForTelegram(status);\n\n  await reply(formatted);\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2.5 Enhanced Logs Handler (`src/bot/commands/handlers/logs.js`)\n\n**增强现有处理器**:\n\n```javascript\nexport async function handleLogs(handlerCtx) {\n  const { reply, replyFile, params } = handlerCtx;\n\n  const pager = createLogPager();\n  const result = await pager.readLogPage(params.type || 'feature', {\n    lines: parseInt(params.lines) || 50,\n    offset: parseInt(params.offset) || 0\n  });\n\n  if (params.file || pager.shouldSendAsFile(result.logs)) {\n    await replyFile(result.logs, `pipeline-logs-${Date.now()}.txt`);\n  } else {\n    const formatted = pager.formatLogsForTelegram(result.logs, result.metadata);\n    await sendChunked(reply, formatted);\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 3. Interface Design\n\n### 3.1 Status Aggregator API\n\n#### `aggregateStatus(type)`\n\n**Input**:\n```typescript\ntype PipelineType = 'feature' | 'bugfix';\n```\n\n**Output**:\n```typescript\ninterface AggregatedStatus {\n  // Basic info\n  stage: 'running' | 'paused' | 'completed' | 'failed' | 'idle';\n  type: PipelineType;\n  timestamp: string;\n\n  // Progress\n  progress: {\n    total: number;\n    completed: number;\n    failed: number;\n    inProgress: number;\n    successRate: number; // percentage\n  };\n\n  // Current execution\n  current?: {\n    featureId: string;\n    startedAt: string;\n    duration: number; // seconds\n  };\n\n  // Last result\n  lastResult?: {\n    runId: string;\n    completedAt: string;\n    status: 'success' | 'failed' | 'partial';\n    summary: string;\n  };\n\n  // Daemon info\n  daemon?: {\n    pid: number;\n    startedAt: string;\n    uptime: number; // seconds\n  };\n\n  // Error summary (if failed)\n  errors?: Array<{\n    featureId: string;\n    errorType: string;\n    message: string;\n  }>;\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3.2 Log Pager API\n\n#### `readLogPage(type, options)`\n\n**Input**:\n```typescript\ninterface LogPageOptions {\n  lines?: number;      // Default: 50, Max: 500\n  offset?: number;     // Default: 0\n  reverse?: boolean;   // Default: true (newest first)\n}\n```\n\n**Output**:\n```typescript\ninterface LogPageResult {\n  ok: boolean;\n  logs: string;\n  metadata: {\n    logPath: string;\n    totalLines: number;\n    pageStart: number;\n    pageEnd: number;\n    requestedLines: number;\n    actualLines: number;\n  };\n  errorCode?: string;\n  message?: string;\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3.3 Telegram Pusher API\n\n#### `pushErrorSummary(type, featureId, error)`\n\n**Input**:\n```typescript\ninterface ErrorSummaryInput {\n  type: PipelineType;\n  featureId: string;\n  error: {\n    type: string;\n    message: string;\n    stack?: string;\n    logLines?: string[];\n  };\n}\n```\n\n**Output**:\n```typescript\ninterface PushResult {\n  ok: boolean;\n  messageId?: string;\n  errorCode?: string;\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 4. Data Model\n\n### 4.1 Aggregated Status Schema\n\n**Internal representation**:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stage\": \"running\",\n  \"type\": \"feature\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T10:30:00Z\",\n  \"progress\": {\n    \"total\": 10,\n    \"completed\": 4,\n    \"failed\": 1,\n    \"inProgress\": 1,\n    \"successRate\": 80.0\n  },\n  \"current\": {\n    \"featureId\": \"F-005\",\n    \"startedAt\": \"2026-03-13T10:25:00Z\",\n    \"duration\": 300\n  },\n  \"daemon\": {\n    \"pid\": 12345,\n    \"startedAt\": \"2026-03-13T10:00:00Z\",\n    \"uptime\": 1800\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 4.2 Log Metadata Schema\n\n```json\n{\n  \"logPath\": \"/path/to/pipeline-daemon.log\",\n  \"totalLines\": 1500,\n  \"pageStart\": 1450,\n  \"pageEnd\": 1500,\n  \"requestedLines\": 50,\n  \"actualLines\": 50\n}\n```\n\n### 4.3 Heartbeat Config Schema\n\n**Path**: `{stateDir}/.heartbeat-config.json` (optional)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"intervalMs\": 30000,\n  \"chatId\": 123456789,\n  \"silentMode\": false,\n  \"errorLinesCount\": 10\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 5. Module Dependencies\n\n```\nstatus-aggregator.js\n    ├── state-manager.js (F-004)\n    ├── pipeline-controller.js (F-004)\n    └── config-loader.js (existing)\n\nlog-pager.js\n    ├── state-manager.js (F-004)\n    └── config-loader.js (existing)\n\ntelegram-pusher.js\n    ├── status-aggregator.js (NEW)\n    ├── log-pager.js (NEW)\n    └── Telegraf bot instance (existing)\n\nstatus.js (handler)\n    └── status-aggregator.js (NEW)\n\nlogs.js (handler)\n    └── log-pager.js (NEW)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 6. Testing Strategy\n\n### 6.1 Unit Tests\n\n| Module | Test File | Focus |\n|--------|-----------|-------|\n| status-aggregator.js | `tests/services/status-aggregator.test.js` | Aggregation logic, progress calculation, formatting |\n| log-pager.js | `tests/services/log-pager.test.js` | Pagination, error extraction, file threshold |\n| telegram-pusher.js | `tests/services/telegram-pusher.test.js` | Throttling, chunking, heartbeat timing |\n\n### 6.2 Integration Tests\n\n**File**: `tests/integration/f005-status-and-logs.integration.test.js`\n\n| Test Case | Description |\n|-----------|-------------|\n| Full Status Flow | Query status for running/idle pipeline |\n| Log Pagination | Read logs with offset/lines parameters |\n| Message Chunking | Verify long messages split correctly |\n| Heartbeat Push | Verify heartbeat triggers and throttles |\n| Error Summary Push | Verify error summary format |\n| Diagnostic Errors | Verify error messages for missing files |\n\n### 6.3 Test Coverage Target\n\n- Core modules: > 85% branch coverage\n- Integration tests: All user stories covered\n\n---\n\n## 7. Risk Assessment\n\n| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation | Owner |\n|------|-------------|--------|------------|-------|\n| Telegram API rate limiting | Medium | Medium | Throttle messages, batch with intervals | Dev |\n| State file race condition | Low | Medium | Read with tolerance for stale data | Dev |\n| Large log file memory | Low | Medium | Stream read with line limit | Dev |\n| Push failure blocking | Low | High | Async queue, fire-and-forget | Dev |\n| Message formatting issues | Low | Low | Template-based formatting, escape special chars | Dev |\n\n---\n\n## 8. User Story to Component Mapping\n\n| User Story | Primary Component | Supporting Components |\n|------------|-------------------|----------------------|\n| US-1: Aggregated Status Query | status-aggregator.js | status.js handler |\n| US-2: Paginated Logs Query | log-pager.js | logs.js handler |\n| US-3: Message Length Compliance | log-pager.js (chunking) | telegram-pusher.js |\n| US-4: Heartbeat Progress Push | telegram-pusher.js | status-aggregator.js |\n| US-5: Error Summary Push | telegram-pusher.js | log-pager.js |\n| US-6: Diagnostic Error Messages | status-aggregator.js, log-pager.js | error-codes.js |\n\n---\n\n## 9. Implementation Phases\n\n### Phase 1: Foundation (T-001 ~ T-009)\n- Setup test infrastructure\n- Create service modules skeleton\n- Define interfaces\n\n### Phase 2: Core Services (T-010 ~ T-099)\n- Implement status-aggregator.js\n- Implement log-pager.js\n- Implement telegram-pusher.js\n\n### Phase 3: User Story Implementation (T-100+)\n- US-1: Aggregated Status Query\n- US-2: Paginated Logs Query\n- US-3: Message Length Compliance\n- US-4: Heartbeat Progress Push\n- US-5: Error Summary Push\n- US-6: Diagnostic Error Messages\n\n### Phase 4: Integration & Polish (T-900+)\n- Integration tests\n- Documentation updates\n- Edge case handling\n\n---\n\n## 10. Key Decisions\n\n| ID | Decision | Rationale |\n|----|----------|-----------|\n| D1 | 独立状态聚合服务 | 保持 pipeline-controller 单一职责，便于测试和扩展 |\n| D2 | 异步消息推送队列 | 推送失败不阻塞主流程，提高可靠性 |\n| D3 | 命令行参数分页 | 简化实现，避免复杂分页协议 |\n| D4 | 定时心跳而非事件监听 | 简化实现，减少与 pipeline 脚本耦合 |\n| D5 | 实时日志错误提取 | 不额外存储错误信息，减少状态管理复杂度 |\n| D6 | 复用现有消息分段机制 | telegram.js 已有 splitMessage，避免重复实现 |\n"}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":48687,"output_tokens":3661,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_25d15181ab0046938b2fac6f","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:04:49.217Z","_requestId":"2a50dd388a364b15840cdcad9dcd8a24"}
