{"type":"assistant","uuid":"20260312040453981af53c48944471","session_id":"da6f98d4-7e33-4c58-9c42-a371874e10ea","message":{"id":"20260312040453981af53c48944471","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"019cde80a0c432218c85dc68c42856ae","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/005-pipeline-status-and-log-streaming/tasks.md","content":"# F-005: Pipeline Status Aggregation and Log Streaming — Task Breakdown\n\n## Phase 1: Setup (T-001 ~ T-009)\n\n- [ ] [T-001] [P] Create test file skeleton for status-aggregator — file: tests/services/status-aggregator.test.js\n- [ ] [T-002] [P] Create test file skeleton for log-pager — file: tests/services/log-pager.test.js\n- [ ] [T-003] [P] Create test file skeleton for telegram-pusher — file: tests/services/telegram-pusher.test.js\n- [ ] [T-004] Create status-aggregator.js module skeleton with interface types — file: src/services/status-aggregator.js\n- [ ] [T-005] Create log-pager.js module skeleton with interface types — file: src/services/log-pager.js\n- [ ] [T-006] Create telegram-pusher.js module skeleton with interface types — file: src/services/telegram-pusher.js\n- [ ] [T-007] [P] Add error codes for status/log operations to error-codes.js — file: src/pipeline-infra/error-codes.js\n- [ ] [T-008] Create integration test skeleton for F-005 — file: tests/integration/f005-status-and-logs.integration.test.js\n- [ ] [T-009] Export new services from index — file: src/services/index.js\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Foundational (T-010 ~ T-099)\n\n### Status Aggregator Core\n\n- [ ] [T-010] Implement aggregateStatus() to read all state sources — file: src/services/status-aggregator.js\n- [ ] [T-011] Implement determinePipelineStage() to classify pipeline state — file: src/services/status-aggregator.js\n- [ ] [T-012] Implement calculateProgress() for completed/failed/inProgress stats — file: src/services/status-aggregator.js\n- [ ] [T-013] Implement getErrorSummary() to extract errors from lastResul