{"type":"user","uuid":"2407c4b4-c0aa-4351-ad80-19c40a444a63","session_id":"da6f98d4-7e33-4c58-9c42-a371874e10ea","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde83497b18f78adb2c6db69ec3b5","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→---\n   2→name: prizm-dev-team-dev\n   3→description: PrizmKit-integrated module implementer (multi-instance). Follows prizmkit.implement workflow with TDD, marks tasks [x] in tasks.md, works within assigned Git worktrees. Use when implementing specific feature modules.\n   4→tools: Read, Write, Edit, Bash, Glob, Grep, TaskCreate, TaskGet, TaskUpdate, TaskList, SendMessage\n   5→model: inherit\n   6→skills: prizmkit-implement, prizmkit-prizm-docs\n   7→---\n   8→\n   9→你是 **Dev Agent**，PrizmKit-integrated Multi-Agent 软件开发协作团队的模块实现者。\n  10→\n  11→### 核心身份\n  12→\n  13→你是团队的\"建筑工人\"——严格按图纸施工，使用 PrizmKit 的 implement 工作流作为执行引擎，专注于：\n  14→- 按照 tasks.md 和 plan.md 中的接口设计逐任务实现功能模块\n  15→- 遵循 TDD 方式开发（测试先行）\n  16→- 完成后立即标记 tasks.md 中的 `[x]`\n  17→- 产出代码和单元测试\n  18→\n  19→### 项目上下文\n  20→\n  21→项目文档在 `.prizm-docs/`。实现前先读 `root.prizm` 了解规则和已知陷阱（TRAPS），修改某模块时读该模块的文档。\n  22→\n  23→### 制品路径\n  24→\n  25→| 路径 | 用途 |\n  26→|------|------|\n  27→| `.prizm-docs/` | 项目知识层 — 规则、模式、已知陷阱 |\n  28→| `.prizmkit/specs/###-feature-name/` | 功能制品 — spec.md / plan.md / tasks.md |\n  29→\n  30→### 必须做 (MUST)\n  31→\n  32→1. 按照分配的任务和 plan.md 中的接口设计实现功能模块\n  33→2. 遵循 TDD 方式：先写测试，再实现，再验证\n  34→3. 产出的代码必须通过本模块的单元测试\n  35→4. 发现接口设计歧义时，立即通过 Coordinator 上报 PM（不自行假设）\n  36→5. 遵循 `prizmkit.implement` 工作流：读取 tasks.md + plan.md + spec.md，逐任务实现\n  37→6. 每个任务完成后**立即**标记 tasks.md 中的 `[x]`（不批量标记）\n  38→7. 实现前读取 `.prizm-docs/` TRAPS 段避免已知陷阱\n  39→8. 检查点任务须验证构建通过和测试通过后才能继续下一阶段\n  40→9. 顺序任务按序执行，失败则停止；并行 `[P]` 任务可继续\n  41→10. 新建子模块时，生成对应的 `.prizm-docs/` L2 文档\n  42→\n  43→### 绝不做 (NEVER)\n  44→\n  45→- 不修改 plan.md 中的接口设计（修改需通过 PM）\n  46→- 不修改其他 Dev Agent 负责的模块代码\n  47→- 不进行集成测试（Reviewer 的职责）\n  48→- 不直接运行 git commit（由 Coordinator 通过 prizmkit.committer 统一提交）\n  49→- 不修改 `.prizmkit/specs/` 中除 `tasks.md`（标记 [x]）以外的任何文件\n  50→- 不为 bug 修复创建新的文档条目；bug 修复是现有功能的完善，应更新原始功能的文档而非在 REGISTRY.md 中创建新条目\n  51→\n  52→### 行为规则\n  53→\n  54→```\n  55→DEV-01: 实现必须严格符合 plan.md 中定义的接口设计\n  56→DEV-02: 每个公开 API/函数必须有对应的单元测试\n  57→DEV-03: 发现接口设计歧义时，不得自行假设，必须上报\n  58→DEV-04: 任务完成后必须运行全部本模块测试\n  59→DEV-05: 代码提交信息遵循 Conventional Commits 格式\n  60→DEV-06: 不得引入未在任务描述中声明的外部依赖\n  61→DEV-07: 遵循 prizmkit.implement 工作流\n  62→DEV-08: 每个任务完成后立即标记 tasks.md [x]\n  63→DEV-09: TDD：先写测试 → 再实现 → 再验证\n  64→DEV-10: 实现每个模块前必须读取 .prizm-docs/ TRAPS 段\n  65→DEV-11: 检查点任务必须验证构建通过和测试通过\n  66→DEV-12: 新建子模块时生成 L2 .prizm-docs/ 文档\n  67→```\n  68→\n  69→### 工作流程\n  70→\n  71→1. 接收任务分配\n  72→2. 读取 `.prizm-docs/root.prizm` 和相关模块文档\n  73→3. 读取 `.prizmkit/specs/###-feature-name/` 中的 `tasks.md`、`plan.md`、`spec.md`\n  74→4. 对每个分配的任务，按 tasks.md 顺序执行：\n  75→   a. 读取目标文件模块的文档（检查 TRAPS 和 DECISIONS）\n  76→   b. TDD：基于验收标准编写测试 → 实现功能代码 → 运行测试验证\n  77→   c. 在 tasks.md 中标记该任务为 `[x]`\n  78→   d. 发送 STATUS_UPDATE 给 Coordinator\n  79→5. 如遇检查点任务，验证构建通过和测试通过后才继续\n  80→6. 遇到接口设计歧义，发送 ESCALATION（不自行假设）\n  81→7. 如新建了子模块，生成对应 `.prizm-docs/` L2 文档\n  82→8. 发送 COMPLETION_SIGNAL\n  83→\n  84→### 异常处理\n  85→\n  86→| 场景 | 策略 |\n  87→|------|------|\n  88→| 接口设计歧义 | 标记 BLOCKED → ESCALATION → 等待 PM 裁定 |\n  89→| 单元测试失败 | 最多重试修复 3 次 → 仍失败则 ISSUE_REPORT |\n  90→| 外部依赖不可用 | 使用 Mock → 标注说明 |\n  91→| 任务超出预估 | ESCALATION → 建议 PM 拆分任务 |\n  92→\n  93→### 通信规则\n  94→\n  95→允许 Agent 之间直接通信，但关键消息和结论必须通知 Coordinator。\n  96→- 发送 STATUS_UPDATE 汇报每个子任务完成\n  97→- 发送 COMPLETION_SIGNAL 标志所有任务完成\n  98→- 发送 ESCALATION 上报接口歧义或任务阻塞\n  99→- 接收 TASK_ASSIGNMENT 获取分配的工作\n 100→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_8d8fb4ee010f4820805a4013","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:07:53.977Z","_requestId":"2a50dd388a364b15840cdcad9dcd8a24"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"442aca6c-534e-4302-aa66-bda04d57d23e","session_id":"da6f98d4-7e33-4c58-9c42-a371874e10ea","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde834b31edc2fc584aaf2515c69e","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→DOC_LEVEL: L0\n   2→PROJECT_NAME: PrizmClaw\n   3→PROJECT_TYPE: telegram-bridge + web-api\n   4→ADOPTION_MODE: brownfield\n   5→PLATFORM: codebuddy\n   6→LANGUAGES: JavaScript(ESM), HTML, CSS, Python, Shell\n   7→PACKAGE_MANAGER: npm\n   8→ENTRYPOINTS: src/index.js -> src/http/server.js + src/bot/telegram.js\n   9→DOC_STATUS: initialized\n  10→ASSESSMENT: ASSESSMENT.md\n  11→MIGRATION_CANDIDATE: docs/AI_CONTEXT -> not_found\n  12→\n  13→MODULE_INDEX:\n  14→- runtime: src/** -> .prizm-docs/runtime.prizm\n  15→- web-ui: public/** -> .prizm-docs/web-ui.prizm\n  16→- pipeline: dev-pipeline/** -> .prizm-docs/pipeline.prizm\n  17→- dev-team: dev-team/** -> .prizm-docs/team.prizm\n  18→- project-config: package.json,.env.example,.codebuddy/settings.json,CODEBUDDY.md -> .prizm-docs/config.prizm\n  19→\n  20→LOAD_RULES:\n  21→- ON_SESSION_START: read .prizm-docs/root.prizm\n  22→- ON_TASK: load related L1 via MODULE_INDEX\n  23→- ON_EDIT: load/create related L2 lazily\n  24→\n  25→DEPENDENCY_HEALTH:\n  26→- outdated_major: dotenv,express,zod\n  27→- npm_audit_prod: 0 vulnerabilities\n  28→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_8d8fb4ee010f4820805a4013","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:07:53.977Z","_requestId":"2a50dd388a364b15840cdcad9dcd8a24"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"efdf420b-e54d-469f-befb-49af51768c5e","session_id":"da6f98d4-7e33-4c58-9c42-a371874e10ea","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde834ccbd08ba49875af27e38bb6","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# F-005: Pipeline Status Aggregation and Log Streaming — Technical Plan\n   2→\n   3→## 1. Architecture Overview\n   4→\n   5→```\n   6→┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n   7→│                         Telegram Command Router (F-002)                      │\n   8→│                    src/bot/commands/handlers/status.js                       │\n   9→│                    src/bot/commands/handlers/logs.js                          │\n  10→└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n  11→                                      │\n  12→                                      ▼\n  13→┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n  14→│                      Status Aggregator (NEW)                                 │\n  15→│                    src/services/status-aggregator.js                         │\n  16→│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐    │\n  17→│  │ • aggregateStatus()   • formatStatusForTelegram()                   │    │\n  18→│  │ • calculateProgress() • getErrorSummary()                           │    │\n  19→│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘    │\n  20→└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n  21→                                      │\n  22→                                      ▼\n  23→┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n  24→│                       Log Pager (NEW)                                        │\n  25→│                    src/services/log-pager.js                                 │\n  26→│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐    │\n  27→│  │ • readLogPage()       • formatLogsForTelegram()                     │    │\n  28→│  │ • extractErrorLines() • shouldSendAsFile()                          │    │\n  29→│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘    │\n  30→└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n  31→                                      │\n  32→                                      ▼\n  33→┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n  34→│                    Telegram Pusher (NEW)                                     │\n  35→│                    src/services/telegram-pusher.js                           │\n  36→│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐    │\n  37→│  │ • pushHeartbeat()     • pushErrorSummary()                          │    │\n  38→│  │ • sendMessageChunked() • throttle()                                 │    │\n  39→│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘    │\n  40→└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n  41→                    │                      │\n  42→                    ▼                      ▼\n  43→┌─────────────────────────┐ ┌─────────────────────────┐\n  44→│   State Manager (F-004) │ │  Pipeline Controller    │\n  45→│    state-manager.js     │ │  pipeline-controller.js │\n  46→├─────────────────────────┤ ├─────────────────────────┤\n  47→│ • readDaemonMeta()      │ │ • getStatus()           │\n  48→│ • readPipelineState()   │ │ • getLogs()             │\n  49→│ • getLastResult()       │ │                         │\n  50→└─────────────────────────┘ └─────────────────────────┘\n  51→                    │                      │\n  52→                    └──────────────────────┘\n  53→                                           ▼\n  54→                    ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n  55→                    │                       State Files                       │\n  56→                    │  state/pipeline.json, state/.pipeline-meta.json        │\n  57→                    │  state/pipeline-daemon.log, state/.last-result.json    │\n  58→                    │  bugfix-state/... (mirror structure)                    │\n  59→                    └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n  60→```\n  61→\n  62→---\n  63→\n  64→## 2. Component Design\n  65→\n  66→### 2.1 Status Aggregator (`src/services/status-aggregator.js`)\n  67→\n  68→**职责**: 聚合多个状态源，生成结构化的状态报告\n  69→\n  70→**核心方法**:\n  71→\n  72→```javascript\n  73→export function createStatusAggregator(options = {}) {\n  74→  const {\n  75→    stateManager = getDefaultStateManager(),\n  76→    pipelineController = getDefaultPipelineController(),\n  77→    config = loadPipelineInfraConfig()\n  78→  } = options;\n  79→\n  80→  return {\n  81→    // Main aggregation\n  82→    async aggregateStatus(type),\n  83→\n  84→    // Formatting\n  85→    formatStatusForTelegram(status),\n  86→\n  87→    // Helpers\n  88→    calculateProgress(state),\n  89→    getErrorSummary(lastResult),\n  90→    determinePipelineStage(state, daemonMeta),\n  91→  };\n  92→}\n  93→```\n  94→\n  95→**状态聚合流程**:\n  96→1. 读取 `pipeline.json` 获取运行状态\n  97→2. 读取 `.pipeline-meta.json` 获取 daemon 信息\n  98→3. 读取 `.last-result.json` 获取历史结果\n  99→4. 读取 `current-session.json` 获取当前 feature\n 100→5. 聚合生成统一的状态对象\n 101→\n 102→---\n 103→\n 104→### 2.2 Log Pager (`src/services/log-pager.js`)\n 105→\n 106→**职责**: 分页读取日志，支持偏移和行数限制\n 107→\n 108→**核心方法**:\n 109→\n 110→```javascript\n 111→export function createLogPager(options = {}) {\n 112→  const {\n 113→    stateManager = getDefaultStateManager(),\n 114→    config = loadPipelineInfraConfig()\n 115→  } = options;\n 116→\n 117→  return {\n 118→    // Main reading\n 119→    async readLogPage(type, options),\n 120→\n 121→    // Formatting\n 122→    formatLogsForTelegram(logs, metadata),\n 123→\n 124→    // Helpers\n 125→    extractErrorLines(logs, lineCount),\n 126→    shouldSendAsFile(logs, thresholdBytes),\n 127→    buildLogMetadata(logPath, totalLines, pageStart, pageEnd),\n 128→  };\n 129→}\n 130→```\n 131→\n 132→**日志读取流程**:\n 133→1. 解析分页参数 (lines, offset)\n 134→2. 读取日志文件（流式读取大文件）\n 135→3. 提取指定范围\n 136→4. 生成格式化输出\n 137→\n 138→---\n 139→\n 140→### 2.3 Telegram Pusher (`src/services/telegram-pusher.js`)\n 141→\n 142→**职责**: 管理 Telegram 消息推送，包括心跳和错误摘要\n 143→\n 144→**核心方法**:\n 145→\n 146→```javascript\n 147→export function createTelegramPusher(options = {}) {\n 148→  const {\n 149→    bot,\n 150→    targetChatId,\n 151→    heartbeatInterval = 30 * 1000, // 30 seconds\n 152→    errorLinesCount = 10,\n 153→    throttleInterval = 30 * 1000,\n 154→  } = options;\n 155→\n 156→  return {\n 157→    // Heartbeat\n 158→    startHeartbeat(type, aggregator),\n 159→    stopHeartbeat(type),\n 160→\n 161→    // Error push\n 162→    async pushErrorSummary(type, featureId, error),\n 163→\n 164→    // Message sending\n 165→    async sendMessageChunked(chatId, text),\n 166→    async sendFile(chatId, content, filename),\n 167→\n 168→    // Throttling\n 169→    throttle(key, fn),\n 170→  };\n 171→}\n 172→```\n 173→\n 174→**推送流程**:\n 175→1. Pipeline 启动时调用 `startHeartbeat`\n 176→2. 定时检查状态并推送进度\n 177→3. 收到错误事件时调用 `pushErrorSummary`\n 178→4. Pipeline 停止时调用 `stopHeartbeat`\n 179→\n 180→---\n 181→\n 182→### 2.4 Enhanced Status Handler (`src/bot/commands/handlers/status.js`)\n 183→\n 184→**增强现有处理器**:\n 185→\n 186→```javascript\n 187→export async function handleStatus(handlerCtx) {\n 188→  const { reply, params } = handlerCtx;\n 189→  const pipelineType = params.type || 'feature';\n 190→\n 191→  const aggregator = createStatusAggregator();\n 192→  const status = await aggregator.aggregateStatus(pipelineType);\n 193→  const formatted = aggregator.formatStatusForTelegram(status);\n 194→\n 195→  await reply(formatted);\n 196→}\n 197→```\n 198→\n 199→---\n 200→\n 201→### 2.5 Enhanced Logs Handler (`src/bot/commands/handlers/logs.js`)\n 202→\n 203→**增强现有处理器**:\n 204→\n 205→```javascript\n 206→export async function handleLogs(handlerCtx) {\n 207→  const { reply, replyFile, params } = handlerCtx;\n 208→\n 209→  const pager = createLogPager();\n 210→  const result = await pager.readLogPage(params.type || 'feature', {\n 211→    lines: parseInt(params.lines) || 50,\n 212→    offset: parseInt(params.offset) || 0\n 213→  });\n 214→\n 215→  if (params.file || pager.shouldSendAsFile(result.logs)) {\n 216→    await replyFile(result.logs, `pipeline-logs-${Date.now()}.txt`);\n 217→  } else {\n 218→    const formatted = pager.formatLogsForTelegram(result.logs, result.metadata);\n 219→    await sendChunked(reply, formatted);\n 220→  }\n 221→}\n 222→```\n 223→\n 224→---\n 225→\n 226→## 3. Interface Design\n 227→\n 228→### 3.1 Status Aggregator API\n 229→\n 230→#### `aggregateStatus(type)`\n 231→\n 232→**Input**:\n 233→```typescript\n 234→type PipelineType = 'feature' | 'bugfix';\n 235→```\n 236→\n 237→**Output**:\n 238→```typescript\n 239→interface AggregatedStatus {\n 240→  // Basic info\n 241→  stage: 'running' | 'paused' | 'completed' | 'failed' | 'idle';\n 242→  type: PipelineType;\n 243→  timestamp: string;\n 244→\n 245→  // Progress\n 246→  progress: {\n 247→    total: number;\n 248→    completed: number;\n 249→    failed: number;\n 250→    inProgress: number;\n 251→    successRate: number; // percentage\n 252→  };\n 253→\n 254→  // Current execution\n 255→  current?: {\n 256→    featureId: string;\n 257→    startedAt: string;\n 258→    duration: number; // seconds\n 259→  };\n 260→\n 261→  // Last result\n 262→  lastResult?: {\n 263→    runId: string;\n 264→    completedAt: string;\n 265→    status: 'success' | 'failed' | 'partial';\n 266→    summary: string;\n 267→  };\n 268→\n 269→  // Daemon info\n 270→  daemon?: {\n 271→    pid: number;\n 272→    startedAt: string;\n 273→    uptime: number; // seconds\n 274→  };\n 275→\n 276→  // Error summary (if failed)\n 277→  errors?: Array<{\n 278→    featureId: string;\n 279→    errorType: string;\n 280→    message: string;\n 281→  }>;\n 282→}\n 283→```\n 284→\n 285→---\n 286→\n 287→### 3.2 Log Pager API\n 288→\n 289→#### `readLogPage(type, options)`\n 290→\n 291→**Input**:\n 292→```typescript\n 293→interface LogPageOptions {\n 294→  lines?: number;      // Default: 50, Max: 500\n 295→  offset?: number;     // Default: 0\n 296→  reverse?: boolean;   // Default: true (newest first)\n 297→}\n 298→```\n 299→\n 300→**Output**:\n 301→```typescript\n 302→interface LogPageResult {\n 303→  ok: boolean;\n 304→  logs: string;\n 305→  metadata: {\n 306→    logPath: string;\n 307→    totalLines: number;\n 308→    pageStart: number;\n 309→    pageEnd: number;\n 310→    requestedLines: number;\n 311→    actualLines: number;\n 312→  };\n 313→  errorCode?: string;\n 314→  message?: string;\n 315→}\n 316→```\n 317→\n 318→---\n 319→\n 320→### 3.3 Telegram Pusher API\n 321→\n 322→#### `pushErrorSummary(type, featureId, error)`\n 323→\n 324→**Input**:\n 325→```typescript\n 326→interface ErrorSummaryInput {\n 327→  type: PipelineType;\n 328→  featureId: string;\n 329→  error: {\n 330→    type: string;\n 331→    message: string;\n 332→    stack?: string;\n 333→    logLines?: string[];\n 334→  };\n 335→}\n 336→```\n 337→\n 338→**Output**:\n 339→```typescript\n 340→interface PushResult {\n 341→  ok: boolean;\n 342→  messageId?: string;\n 343→  errorCode?: string;\n 344→}\n 345→```\n 346→\n 347→---\n 348→\n 349→## 4. Data Model\n 350→\n 351→### 4.1 Aggregated Status Schema\n 352→\n 353→**Internal representation**:\n 354→\n 355→```json\n 356→{\n 357→  \"stage\": \"running\",\n 358→  \"type\": \"feature\",\n 359→  \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T10:30:00Z\",\n 360→  \"progress\": {\n 361→    \"total\": 10,\n 362→    \"completed\": 4,\n 363→    \"failed\": 1,\n 364→    \"inProgress\": 1,\n 365→    \"successRate\": 80.0\n 366→  },\n 367→  \"current\": {\n 368→    \"featureId\": \"F-005\",\n 369→    \"startedAt\": \"2026-03-13T10:25:00Z\",\n 370→    \"duration\": 300\n 371→  },\n 372→  \"daemon\": {\n 373→    \"pid\": 12345,\n 374→    \"startedAt\": \"2026-03-13T10:00:00Z\",\n 375→    \"uptime\": 1800\n 376→  }\n 377→}\n 378→```\n 379→\n 380→### 4.2 Log Metadata Schema\n 381→\n 382→```json\n 383→{\n 384→  \"logPath\": \"/path/to/pipeline-daemon.log\",\n 385→  \"totalLines\": 1500,\n 386→  \"pageStart\": 1450,\n 387→  \"pageEnd\": 1500,\n 388→  \"requestedLines\": 50,\n 389→  \"actualLines\": 50\n 390→}\n 391→```\n 392→\n 393→### 4.3 Heartbeat Config Schema\n 394→\n 395→**Path**: `{stateDir}/.heartbeat-config.json` (optional)\n 396→\n 397→```json\n 398→{\n 399→  \"enabled\": true,\n 400→  \"intervalMs\": 30000,\n 401→  \"chatId\": 123456789,\n 402→  \"silentMode\": false,\n 403→  \"errorLinesCount\": 10\n 404→}\n 405→```\n 406→\n 407→---\n 408→\n 409→## 5. Module Dependencies\n 410→\n 411→```\n 412→status-aggregator.js\n 413→    ├── state-manager.js (F-004)\n 414→    ├── pipeline-controller.js (F-004)\n 415→    └── config-loader.js (existing)\n 416→\n 417→log-pager.js\n 418→    ├── state-manager.js (F-004)\n 419→    └── config-loader.js (existing)\n 420→\n 421→telegram-pusher.js\n 422→    ├── status-aggregator.js (NEW)\n 423→    ├── log-pager.js (NEW)\n 424→    └── Telegraf bot instance (existing)\n 425→\n 426→status.js (handler)\n 427→    └── status-aggregator.js (NEW)\n 428→\n 429→logs.js (handler)\n 430→    └── log-pager.js (NEW)\n 431→```\n 432→\n 433→---\n 434→\n 435→## 6. Testing Strategy\n 436→\n 437→### 6.1 Unit Tests\n 438→\n 439→| Module | Test File | Focus |\n 440→|--------|-----------|-------|\n 441→| status-aggregator.js | `tests/services/status-aggregator.test.js` | Aggregation logic, progress calculation, formatting |\n 442→| log-pager.js | `tests/services/log-pager.test.js` | Pagination, error extraction, file threshold |\n 443→| telegram-pusher.js | `tests/services/telegram-pusher.test.js` | Throttling, chunking, heartbeat timing |\n 444→\n 445→### 6.2 Integration Tests\n 446→\n 447→**File**: `tests/integration/f005-status-and-logs.integration.test.js`\n 448→\n 449→| Test Case | Description |\n 450→|-----------|-------------|\n 451→| Full Status Flow | Query status for running/idle pipeline |\n 452→| Log Pagination | Read logs with offset/lines parameters |\n 453→| Message Chunking | Verify long messages split correctly |\n 454→| Heartbeat Push | Verify heartbeat triggers and throttles |\n 455→| Error Summary Push | Verify error summary format |\n 456→| Diagnostic Errors | Verify error messages for missing files |\n 457→\n 458→### 6.3 Test Coverage Target\n 459→\n 460→- Core modules: > 85% branch coverage\n 461→- Integration tests: All user stories covered\n 462→\n 463→---\n 464→\n 465→## 7. Risk Assessment\n 466→\n 467→| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation | Owner |\n 468→|------|-------------|--------|------------|-------|\n 469→| Telegram API rate limiting | Medium | Medium | Throttle messages, batch with intervals | Dev |\n 470→| State file race condition | Low | Medium | Read with tolerance for stale data | Dev |\n 471→| Large log file memory | Low | Medium | Stream read with line limit | Dev |\n 472→| Push failure blocking | Low | High | Async queue, fire-and-forget | Dev |\n 473→| Message formatting issues | Low | Low | Template-based formatting, escape special chars | Dev |\n 474→\n 475→---\n 476→\n 477→## 8. User Story to Component Mapping\n 478→\n 479→| User Story | Primary Component | Supporting Components |\n 480→|------------|-------------------|----------------------|\n 481→| US-1: Aggregated Status Query | status-aggregator.js | status.js handler |\n 482→| US-2: Paginated Logs Query | log-pager.js | logs.js handler |\n 483→| US-3: Message Length Compliance | log-pager.js (chunking) | telegram-pusher.js |\n 484→| US-4: Heartbeat Progress Push | telegram-pusher.js | status-aggregator.js |\n 485→| US-5: Error Summary Push | telegram-pusher.js | log-pager.js |\n 486→| US-6: Diagnostic Error Messages | status-aggregator.js, log-pager.js | error-codes.js |\n 487→\n 488→---\n 489→\n 490→## 9. Implementation Phases\n 491→\n 492→### Phase 1: Foundation (T-001 ~ T-009)\n 493→- Setup test infrastructure\n 494→- Create service modules skeleton\n 495→- Define interfaces\n 496→\n 497→### Phase 2: Core Services (T-010 ~ T-099)\n 498→- Implement status-aggregator.js\n 499→- Implement log-pager.js\n 500→- Implement telegram-pusher.js\n 501→\n 502→### Phase 3: User Story Implementation (T-100+)\n 503→- US-1: Aggregated Status Query\n 504→- US-2: Paginated Logs Query\n 505→- US-3: Message Length Compliance\n 506→- US-4: Heartbeat Progress Push\n 507→- US-5: Error Summary Push\n 508→- US-6: Diagnostic Error Messages\n 509→\n 510→### Phase 4: Integration & Polish (T-900+)\n 511→- Integration tests\n 512→- Documentation updates\n 513→- Edge case handling\n 514→\n 515→---\n 516→\n 517→## 10. Key Decisions\n 518→\n 519→| ID | Decision | Rationale |\n 520→|----|----------|-----------|\n 521→| D1 | 独立状态聚合服务 | 保持 pipeline-controller 单一职责，便于测试和扩展 |\n 522→| D2 | 异步消息推送队列 | 推送失败不阻塞主流程，提高可靠性 |\n 523→| D3 | 命令行参数分页 | 简化实现，避免复杂分页协议 |\n 524→| D4 | 定时心跳而非事件监听 | 简化实现，减少与 pipeline 脚本耦合 |\n 525→| D5 | 实时日志错误提取 | 不额外存储错误信息，减少状态管理复杂度 |\n 526→| D6 | 复用现有消息分段机制 | telegram.js 已有 splitMessage，避免重复实现 |\n 527→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_8d8fb4ee010f4820805a4013","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:07:53.978Z","_requestId":"2a50dd388a364b15840cdcad9dcd8a24"}
