d | Aliases | Description |\n  79→|---------|---------|-------------|\n  80→| `/pipeline` | `/p` | Manage pipelines (run/status/logs/stop) |\n  81→| `/bugfix` | `/b` | Start bugfix pipeline |\n  82→| `/planner` | — | Manage planner pipelines |\n  83→| `/status` | `/s` | Show running pipelines |\n  84→| `/logs` | `/l` | View pipeline logs |\n  85→| `/stop` | — | Stop running pipelines |\n  86→\n  87→### Verification\n  88→\n  89→- `npm test`: 105 tests pass (76 for F-002)\n  90→- Code review: PASS\n  91→- All 21 tasks completed\n  92→\n  93→---\n  94→\n  95→## F-003: Feature and Bug Plan Ingestion\n  96→\n  97→**Status:** completed  \n  98→**Completion Date:** 2026-03-12\n  99→\n 100→### Deliverables\n 101→\n 102→- `src/services/plan-ingestion-service.js` - Schema validation, version management, plan registry\n 103→- `src/bot/commands/handlers/plan.js` - Plan command handler (status/versions/use/rollback/validate)\n 104→- `src/bot/telegram.js` - Document upload handler for JSON files\n 105→- `src/services/pipeline-control-service.js` - Extended with resolvePlanListPath()\n 106→- `src/pipeline-infra/config-loader.js` - Extended with plansDir config\n 107→- `plans/` directory structure with feature-list/ and bug-fix-list/ subdirectories\n 108→- Unit tests in `tests/services/plan-ingestion-service.test.js`\n 109→- Integration tests in `tests/integration/f003-plan-ingestion.integration.test.js`\n 110→\n 111→### Acceptance Criteria Met\n 112→\n 113→- US-1: Upload Plan File - Telegram document message handling with auto-type detection\n 114→- US-2: Schema Validation - Ajv-based validation with field-level error messages\n 115→- US-3: Version Management - Timestamp-based versioning with use/rollback commands\n 116→- US-4: Plan Status Query - Status command showing version info and content summary\n 117→- US-5: Plan Integrity Protection - Validation precedes save, current version preserved on error\n 118→- US-6: Pipeline Integration - resolvePlanListPath() for dynamic plan p