{"type":"user","uuid":"f5e8504e-29f8-4782-9964-3511798a5e40","session_id":"da6f98d4-7e33-4c58-9c42-a371874e10ea","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_8d8fb4ee010f4820805a4013","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tasks for F-005 have been implemented successfully. Here's a summary of what was accomplished:\n\n## F-005: Pipeline Status Aggregation and Log Streaming - Implementation Complete\n\n### New Modules Created\n\n1. **`src/services/status-aggregator.js`** - Aggregates pipeline status from multiple state sources\n   - `aggregateStatus()` - Reads all state sources and generates unified status\n   - `determinePipelineStage()` - Classifies pipeline state (running/paused/completed/failed/idle)\n   - `calculateProgress()` - Computes completed/failed/inProgress statistics\n   - `getErrorSummary()` - Extracts errors from last result\n   - `formatStatusForTelegram()` - Formats status for human-readable output\n\n2. **`src/services/log-pager.js`** - Paginated log reading\n   - `readLogPage()` - Reads logs with offset/lines parameters\n   - `extractErrorLines()` - Extracts ERROR lines from logs\n   - `shouldSendAsFile()` - Threshold check for file sending\n   - `formatLogsForTelegram()` - Formats logs with metadata header\n   - `buildLogMetadata()` - Creates page metadata object\n\n3. **`src/services/telegram-pusher.js`** - Telegram message pushing\n   - `startHeartbeat()` / `stopHeartbeat()` - Periodic status updates\n   - `pushErrorSummary()` - Error notifications with execution time\n   - `pushStartupNotification()` - Startup notifications with runId and target list\n   - `sendMessageChunked()` - Auto-chunking with [N/M] segment numbering\n   - `sendFile()` - File attachment support\n   - `throttle()` - Rate limiting mechanism\n\n### Updated Files\n\n- **`src/bot/commands/handlers/status.js`** - Enhanced with `--type` parameter support\n- **`src/bot/commands/handlers/logs.js`** - Enhanced with `--lines`, `--offset`, `--type`, `--file` parameters\n- **`src/pipeline-infra/config-loader.js`** - Added heartbeat config options (HEARTBEAT_ENABLED, HEARTBEAT_CHAT_ID, HEARTBEAT_INTERVAL_MS, SILENT_MODE, ERROR_LINES_COUNT)\n- **`src/pipeline-infra/error-codes.js`** - Added 8 new error codes for F-005\n- **`src/services/pipeline-controller.js`** - Added lifecycle event emitter for heartbeat integration\n- **`src/services/index.js`** - Created to export all services\n\n### Tests Created\n\n- `tests/services/status-aggregator.test.js`\n- `tests/services/log-pager.test.js`\n- `tests/services/telegram-pusher.test.js`\n- `tests/integration/f005-status-and-logs.integration.test.js`\n\n### Documentation Updated\n\n- `.prizm-docs/runtime/services.prizm`\n- `.prizm-docs/runtime/bot.prizm`\n- `.prizm-docs/changelog.prizm`\n- `.prizmkit/specs/REGISTRY.md`\n\n### HIGH Issues Addressed\n\n1. ✅ **AC-4.1**: Startup notification includes runId and target list\n2. ✅ **AC-4.5**: Full heartbeat config options (HEARTBEAT_ENABLED, HEARTBEAT_CHAT_ID, HEARTBEAT_INTERVAL_MS, SILENT_MODE, ERROR_LINES_COUNT)\n3. ✅ **AC-5.3**: Error summary message format includes execution time/duration\n\n[Agent ID: agent-45a1318b]"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_8d8fb4ee010f4820805a4013","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:22:06.547Z","_requestId":"2a50dd388a364b15840cdcad9dcd8a24"}
