{"type":"assistant","uuid":"2026031204221591df229830294e92","session_id":"da6f98d4-7e33-4c58-9c42-a371874e10ea","message":{"id":"2026031204221591df229830294e92","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"019cde908890aba8f9073d1305fbec92","name":"Read","input":{"file_path":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/005-pipeline-status-and-log-streaming/tasks.md"}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":10937,"output_tokens":310,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_475ad05a155d4431bd73ba2b","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:22:20.663Z","_requestId":"2a50dd388a364b15840cdcad9dcd8a24"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"c9fcca83-8dab-4346-9128-5f415616088b","session_id":"da6f98d4-7e33-4c58-9c42-a371874e10ea","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde90815e663126210da71e419dc4","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→---\n   2→name: prizm-dev-team-reviewer\n   3→description: PrizmKit-integrated quality reviewer. Uses prizmkit.analyze for cross-document consistency, prizmkit.code-review for spec compliance and code quality, and writes integration tests. Use when performing analysis, testing, or code review.\n   4→tools: Read, Write, Edit, Bash, Glob, Grep, TaskCreate, TaskGet, TaskUpdate, TaskList, SendMessage\n   5→model: inherit\n   6→skills: prizmkit-code-review, prizmkit-analyze, prizmkit-prizm-docs\n   7→---\n   8→\n   9→你是 **Reviewer Agent**，PrizmKit-integrated Multi-Agent 软件开发协作团队的质量审查员。\n  10→\n  11→### 核心身份\n  12→\n  13→你是团队的\"质检员 + 校对员\"——不生产产品但确保质量，负责两个阶段的工作：\n  14→1. **交叉校验（Phase 4）**: 在实现前用 `prizmkit.analyze` 检查 spec/plan/tasks 的一致性\n  15→2. **评审（Phase 6）**: 在实现后用 `prizmkit.code-review` 检查代码质量，编写和执行集成测试\n  16→\n  17→### 项目上下文\n  18→\n  19→项目文档在 `.prizm-docs/`。审查前先读 `root.prizm` 了解项目规则（RULES）、模式（PATTERNS）和已知陷阱（TRAPS），需要时读取模块级文档。\n  20→\n  21→### 制品路径\n  22→\n  23→| 路径 | 用途 |\n  24→|------|------|\n  25→| `.prizm-docs/` | 项目知识层 — 规则、模式、已知陷阱 |\n  26→| `.prizmkit/specs/###-feature-name/` | 功能制品 — spec.md / plan.md / tasks.md |\n  27→\n  28→### 必须做 (MUST)\n  29→\n  30→1. Phase 4 时运行 `prizmkit.analyze` 做交叉一致性校验\n  31→2. Phase 6 时运行 `prizmkit.code-review` 做规格合规和代码质量审查\n  32→3. Phase 6 时编写和执行集成测试，验证模块间交互\n  33→4. 验证实际实现是否符合 plan.md 中的接口设计\n  34→5. 验证跨模块数据流的完整性和正确性\n  35→6. 测试边界条件和异常路径\n  36→7. 检查代码是否符合 `.prizm-docs/` RULES 和 PATTERNS\n  37→8. 审查是**只读操作**（Phase 4 和 Phase 6 的审查部分不修改代码文件）\n  38→9. 集成测试用例必须覆盖 spec.md 定义的所有用户故事\n  39→\n  40→### 绝不做 (NEVER)\n  41→\n  42→- 不编写实现代码（Dev 的职责）\n  43→- 不分解任务（PM 的职责）\n  44→- 不进行任务调度（Coordinator 的职责）\n  45→\n  46→### 行为规则\n  47→\n  48→```\n  49→REV-01: Phase 4 使用 prizmkit.analyze 做交叉校验\n  50→REV-02: Phase 6 使用 prizmkit.code-review 做代码审查\n  51→REV-03: 每个发现必须引用具体的文件路径和行号\n  52→REV-04: CRITICAL 级别发现必须包含具体的修复建议\n  53→REV-05: 最多 30 个发现（保持可操作性）\n  54→REV-06: Spec compliance 失败始终为 HIGH 或 CRITICAL\n  55→REV-07: 安全发现始终为 HIGH 或 CRITICAL\n  56→REV-08: 集成测试必须覆盖 spec.md 所有用户故事\n  57→REV-09: 审查代码是否符合 .prizm-docs/ PATTERNS 和 RULES\n  58→```\n  59→\n  60→### Phase 4 工作流程：交叉校验\n  61→\n  62→**前置条件**: PM 已完成 spec.md / plan.md / tasks.md\n  63→\n  64→1. 运行 `prizmkit.analyze`（只读）\n  65→   - 输入: spec.md, plan.md, tasks.md\n  66→   - 6 个检测通道: 重复检测、歧义检测、不完整检测、Prizm 规则对齐、覆盖缺口、不一致性\n  67→   - 输出: 一致性分析报告（仅对话输出）\n  68→2. 如发现 CRITICAL 问题，报告给 Coordinator 退回 PM 修复\n  69→3. 发送 COMPLETION_SIGNAL（含分析结果）\n  70→\n  71→### Phase 6 工作流程：评审\n  72→\n  73→**前置条件**: Dev 已完成实现，所有任务标记 `[x]`\n  74→\n  75→1. 读取 `.prizm-docs/root.prizm`，重点关注 RULES 和 PATTERNS\n  76→2. 运行 `prizmkit.code-review`（只读）\n  77→   - 6 个审查维度: 规格符合度、计划遵循度、代码质量、安全性、一致性、测试覆盖\n  78→   - 判定: PASS | PASS WITH WARNINGS | NEEDS FIXES\n  79→3. 编写和执行集成测试:\n  80→   - 接口合规性（请求格式、响应格式）\n  81→   - 跨模块数据流完整性\n  82→   - 用户故事验收标准（来自 spec.md）\n  83→   - 边界条件和异常路径\n  84→4. 生成统一评审报告\n  85→5. 发送 COMPLETION_SIGNAL（含判定结果）\n  86→\n  87→### 判定标准\n  88→\n  89→| 判定 | 条件 | 后续动作 |\n  90→|------|------|---------|\n  91→| **PASS** | 无 CRITICAL 或 HIGH 发现 | 进入下一阶段 |\n  92→| **PASS_WITH_WARNINGS** | 无 CRITICAL，有 HIGH 发现 | 记录待改进项，可进入下一阶段 |\n  93→| **NEEDS_FIXES** | 存在 CRITICAL 发现 | 退回 Dev 修复后重新评审 |\n  94→\n  95→### 严重级别\n  96→\n  97→| 级别 | 定义 | 示例 |\n  98→|------|------|------|\n  99→| CRITICAL | 安全风险或严重架构问题 | SQL 注入、硬编码密钥 |\n 100→| HIGH | 影响可维护性的显著问题 | 规格不符、大量重复代码 |\n 101→| MEDIUM | 代码质量改进点 | 命名不统一、缺少注释 |\n 102→| LOW | 风格建议 | 格式微调、可选优化 |\n 103→\n 104→### 异常处理\n 105→\n 106→| 场景 | 策略 |\n 107→|------|------|\n 108→| analyze 发现 CRITICAL | 报告 Coordinator → 退回 PM 修复 |\n 109→| code-review 发现 CRITICAL | 报告 Coordinator → 退回 Dev 修复 |\n 110→| 集成测试失败 | 分类严重级别 → ISSUE_REPORT → Coordinator 派发给 Dev |\n 111→| 审查发现超过 30 个 | 只保留最严重的 30 个 |\n 112→| Prizm RULES 违规 | 自动标记为 CRITICAL |\n 113→\n 114→### 通信规则\n 115→\n 116→允许 Agent 之间直接通信，但关键消息和结论必须通知 Coordinator。\n 117→- 发送 COMPLETION_SIGNAL（含判定结果）标志完成\n 118→- 发送 ISSUE_REPORT 报告 CRITICAL 发现\n 119→- 接收 TASK_ASSIGNMENT 获取分配的工作\n 120→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_475ad05a155d4431bd73ba2b","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:22:20.663Z","_requestId":"2a50dd388a364b15840cdcad9dcd8a24"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"8976d681-6988-4ccf-a52f-ace05ed47b32","session_id":"da6f98d4-7e33-4c58-9c42-a371874e10ea","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde9082f7ef359df029f06f714bc3","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→DOC_LEVEL: L0\n   2→PROJECT_NAME: PrizmClaw\n   3→PROJECT_TYPE: telegram-bridge + web-api\n   4→ADOPTION_MODE: brownfield\n   5→PLATFORM: codebuddy\n   6→LANGUAGES: JavaScript(ESM), HTML, CSS, Python, Shell\n   7→PACKAGE_MANAGER: npm\n   8→ENTRYPOINTS: src/index.js -> src/http/server.js + src/bot/telegram.js\n   9→DOC_STATUS: initialized\n  10→ASSESSMENT: ASSESSMENT.md\n  11→MIGRATION_CANDIDATE: docs/AI_CONTEXT -> not_found\n  12→\n  13→MODULE_INDEX:\n  14→- runtime: src/** -> .prizm-docs/runtime.prizm\n  15→- web-ui: public/** -> .prizm-docs/web-ui.prizm\n  16→- pipeline: dev-pipeline/** -> .prizm-docs/pipeline.prizm\n  17→- dev-team: dev-team/** -> .prizm-docs/team.prizm\n  18→- project-config: package.json,.env.example,.codebuddy/settings.json,CODEBUDDY.md -> .prizm-docs/config.prizm\n  19→\n  20→LOAD_RULES:\n  21→- ON_SESSION_START: read .prizm-docs/root.prizm\n  22→- ON_TASK: load related L1 via MODULE_INDEX\n  23→- ON_EDIT: load/create related L2 lazily\n  24→\n  25→DEPENDENCY_HEALTH:\n  26→- outdated_major: dotenv,express,zod\n  27→- npm_audit_prod: 0 vulnerabilities\n  28→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_475ad05a155d4431bd73ba2b","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:22:20.664Z","_requestId":"2a50dd388a364b15840cdcad9dcd8a24"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"d7e6c6cf-85dc-4375-8600-674c32defc29","session_id":"da6f98d4-7e33-4c58-9c42-a371874e10ea","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde9084650a2e784027a6f4013345","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# F-005: Pipeline Status Aggregation and Log Streaming\n   2→\n   3→## Summary\n   4→\n   5→实现 pipeline 状态聚合与日志流式回传到 Telegram，包括当前执行 feature、已完成/失败统计、关键错误摘要、日志 tail 分页与节流推送。该功能应兼顾可读性与消息长度限制，避免刷屏并支持按需拉取详细日志。\n   6→\n   7→---\n   8→\n   9→## User Stories\n  10→\n  11→### US-1: Aggregated Status Query\n  12→\n  13→**As a** Telegram 用户  \n  14→**I want** 通过 `/status` 命令获取聚合后的 pipeline 状态信息  \n  15→**So that** 我可以快速了解当前执行阶段、进度统计和关键信息，而不需要查看原始状态文件\n  16→\n  17→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  18→- AC-1.1: `/status` 返回当前 pipeline 阶段（running/paused/completed/failed/idle）\n  19→- AC-1.2: 显示已完成/失败/进行中的 feature 统计\n  20→- AC-1.3: 若有正在执行的 feature，显示其 ID 和开始时间\n  21→- AC-1.4: 显示最近一次运行的结果摘要（成功率、耗时）\n  22→- AC-1.5: 支持指定 pipeline 类型参数 (`/status --type=feature|bugfix`)\n  23→\n  24→---\n  25→\n  26→### US-2: Paginated Logs Query\n  27→\n  28→**As a** Telegram 用户  \n  29→**I want** 通过 `/logs` 命令分页读取日志  \n  30→**So that** 我可以按需获取日志片段而不被过长的输出淹没\n  31→\n  32→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  33→- AC-2.1: `/logs` 默认返回最近 50 行日志\n  34→- AC-2.2: 支持 `--lines=N` 参数指定行数（最大 500 行）\n  35→- AC-2.3: 支持 `--offset=N` 参数跳过前 N 行实现分页\n  36→- AC-2.4: 支持指定 pipeline 类型 (`--type=feature|bugfix`)\n  37→- AC-2.5: 日志不存在时返回友好提示而非错误\n  38→\n  39→---\n  40→\n  41→### US-3: Message Length Compliance\n  42→\n  43→**As a** Telegram 用户  \n  44→**I want** 长日志输出自动分段发送  \n  45→**So that** 我可以收到完整的日志而不会因为 Telegram 消息长度限制而丢失内容\n  46→\n  47→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  48→- AC-3.1: 单条消息超过 4000 字符时自动分段\n  49→- AC-3.2: 每段消息标记序号（如 `[1/3]`）\n  50→- AC-3.3: 分段间隔不小于 500ms，避免触发 Telegram 限流\n  51→- AC-3.4: 提供文件发送选项用于超长日志（`--file` 参数）\n  52→\n  53→---\n  54→\n  55→### US-4: Heartbeat Progress Push\n  56→\n  57→**As a** 运维人员  \n  58→**I want** 在 pipeline 执行期间定期接收进度心跳  \n  59→**So that** 我可以监控执行状态而无需主动查询\n  60→\n  61→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  62→- AC-4.1: Pipeline 启动时推送启动通知（包含 runId、目标列表）\n  63→- AC-4.2: 每 N 个 feature 完成后触发进度推送检查（N 可配置，默认 1）\n  64→- AC-4.3: 进度消息包含已完成/总数、当前 feature、成功率\n  65→- AC-4.4: 消息节流：两次推送间隔至少 30 秒，避免刷屏（即使有多个 feature 完成）\n  66→- AC-4.5: 推送目标为配置的 Telegram chatId\n  67→\n  68→---\n  69→\n  70→### US-5: Error Summary Push\n  71→\n  72→**As a** 运维人员  \n  73→**I want** 在 feature 执行失败时自动接收错误摘要  \n  74→**So that** 我可以快速定位问题并决定是否需要干预\n  75→\n  76→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  77→- AC-5.1: 单个 feature 失败时推送错误摘要（包含 feature ID、错误类型）\n  78→- AC-5.2: 显示错误日志的最后 N 行（可配置，默认 10 行）\n  79→- AC-5.3: 显示 feature 的执行耗时\n  80→- AC-5.4: 支持静默模式配置（只推送关键错误，跳过预期失败）\n  81→\n  82→---\n  83→\n  84→### US-6: Diagnostic Error Messages\n  85→\n  86→**As a** Telegram 用户  \n  87→**I want** 日志读取异常或状态文件缺失时收到可诊断的错误信息  \n  88→**So that** 我可以理解问题原因并采取相应行动\n  89→\n  90→**Acceptance Criteria:**\n  91→- AC-6.1: 状态文件缺失时返回明确提示（如\"Pipeline 尚未初始化\"）\n  92→- AC-6.2: 日志文件不存在时返回友好提示（如\"暂无日志\"）\n  93→- AC-6.3: JSON 解析失败时返回错误类型和文件路径\n  94→- AC-6.4: 错误消息包含诊断建议（如\"请先启动 pipeline\"）\n  95→\n  96→---\n  97→\n  98→## Non-Functional Requirements\n  99→\n 100→### NFR-1: Performance\n 101→- 状态聚合响应时间 < 200ms\n 102→- 日志读取（100 行）< 300ms\n 103→- 消息分段发送不影响主流程\n 104→\n 105→### NFR-2: Reliability\n 106→- 状态推送失败不阻塞 pipeline 执行\n 107→- 消息队列机制确保推送可靠性（内存队列 + 重试）\n 108→- 重试机制处理临时网络错误（最多 3 次，指数退避）\n 109→\n 110→### NFR-3: Maintainability\n 111→- 状态聚合逻辑独立于 pipeline 控制器\n 112→- 消息格式模板化，易于定制\n 113→- 测试覆盖率 > 85%\n 114→\n 115→### NFR-4: Extensibility\n 116→- 支持添加新的状态指标\n 117→- 支持自定义消息模板\n 118→- 支持多种推送渠道（Telegram + 预留扩展）\n 119→\n 120→---\n 121→\n 122→## Scope Boundaries\n 123→\n 124→### In Scope\n 125→- 状态聚合服务 (`src/services/status-aggregator.js`)\n 126→- 日志分页服务 (`src/services/log-pager.js`)\n 127→- Telegram 消息推送服务 (`src/services/telegram-pusher.js`)\n 128→- 进度心跳机制\n 129→- 错误摘要推送\n 130→- `/status` 和 `/logs` 命令增强\n 131→- 消息分段与节流\n 132→- 单元测试与集成测试\n 133→\n 134→### Out of Scope\n 135→- Pipeline 核心执行逻辑修改（算法、调度策略）\n 136→- **例外**: 允许添加最小化的生命周期通知钩子（onPipelineStart/onPipelineStop），用于触发外部心跳服务\n 137→- 数据库持久化（继续使用 JSON 文件）\n 138→- Web UI 状态展示\n 139→- 多租户支持\n 140→- 认证授权（由上层处理）\n 141→\n 142→---\n 143→\n 144→## Dependencies\n 145→\n 146→| Dependency | Type | Status | Notes |\n 147→|------------|------|--------|-------|\n 148→| F-004 | Feature | completed | 提供 pipeline-controller API |\n 149→| F-002 | Feature | completed | 提供 Telegram 命令路由 |\n 150→| Telegraf | Library | installed | Telegram Bot API |\n 151→| state-manager.js | Module | existing | 状态文件读取 |\n 152→| pipeline-controller.js | Module | existing | 管道控制 API |\n 153→\n 154→---\n 155→\n 156→## Risks\n 157→\n 158→| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation |\n 159→|------|-------------|--------|------------|\n 160→| Telegram API 限流 | Medium | Medium | 消息节流、批量发送间隔控制 |\n 161→| 状态文件并发访问冲突 | Low | Medium | 使用锁机制，读取时容忍短暂不一致 |\n 162→| 大日志文件内存占用 | Low | Medium | 流式读取、行数限制 |\n 163→| 消息推送阻塞主流程 | Low | High | 异步推送、失败即丢弃 |\n 164→\n 165→---\n 166→\n 167→## Technical Notes\n 168→\n 169→### 现有基础设施\n 170→- `state-manager.js` 已提供状态文件读取能力\n 171→- `pipeline-controller.js` 提供 getStatus/getLogs API\n 172→- `telegram.js` 已有消息分段机制 (`splitMessage`)\n 173→- 已有 Telegram bot 实例和消息发送能力\n 174→\n 175→### 设计方向\n 176→- 创建独立的 `status-aggregator.js` 聚合状态信息\n 177→- 创建 `log-pager.js` 处理日志分页\n 178→- 创建 `telegram-pusher.js` 处理推送逻辑\n 179→- 复用现有的 message chunking 机制\n 180→- 使用 EventEmitter 或回调实现推送触发\n 181→\n 182→---\n 183→\n 184→## Decisions\n 185→\n 186→| ID | Date | Decision |\n 187→|----|------|----------|\n 188→| D1 | 2026-03-13 | 创建独立的状态聚合服务而非扩展 pipeline-controller，保持单一职责 |\n 189→| D2 | 2026-03-13 | 消息推送使用内存队列 + 重试机制，失败不阻塞主流程 |\n 190→| D3 | 2026-03-13 | 日志分页参数通过命令行解析，不引入复杂分页协议 |\n 191→| D4 | 2026-03-13 | 心跳推送采用事件驱动（feature 完成）+ 时间节流（≥30s），平衡实时性与刷屏控制 |\n 192→| D5 | 2026-03-13 | 错误摘要从日志文件实时提取，不额外存储 |\n 193→| D6 | 2026-03-13 | 允许在 pipeline-controller 添加最小化生命周期钩子（onPipelineStart/onPipelineStop），不修改核心执行逻辑 |\n 194→| D7 | 2026-03-13 | 消息队列重试策略：最多 3 次，指数退避（1s → 2s → 4s），最终失败丢弃消息 |\n 195→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_475ad05a155d4431bd73ba2b","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:22:20.664Z","_requestId":"2a50dd388a364b15840cdcad9dcd8a24"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"de3c5662-b9b7-4ef1-9fcf-808b6b9f5049","session_id":"da6f98d4-7e33-4c58-9c42-a371874e10ea","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde90866c48da2258e00a76d87f02","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# F-005: Pipeline Status Aggregation and Log Streaming — Technical Plan\n   2→\n   3→## 1. Architecture Overview\n   4→\n   5→```\n   6→┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n   7→│                         Telegram Command Router (F-002)                      │\n   8→│                    src/bot/commands/handlers/status.js                       │\n   9→│                    src/bot/commands/handlers/logs.js                          │\n  10→└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n  11→                                      │\n  12→                                      ▼\n  13→┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n  14→│                      Status Aggregator (NEW)                                 │\n  15→│                    src/services/status-aggregator.js                         │\n  16→│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐    │\n  17→│  │ • aggregateStatus()   • formatStatusForTelegram()                   │    │\n  18→│  │ • calculateProgress() • getErrorSummary()                           │    │\n  19→│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘    │\n  20→└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n  21→                                      │\n  22→                                      ▼\n  23→┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n  24→│                       Log Pager (NEW)                                        │\n  25→│                    src/services/log-pager.js                                 │\n  26→│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐    │\n  27→│  │ • readLogPage()       • formatLogsForTelegram()                     │    │\n  28→│  │ • extractErrorLines() • shouldSendAsFile()                          │    │\n  29→│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘    │\n  30→└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n  31→                                      │\n  32→                                      ▼\n  33→┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n  34→│                    Telegram Pusher (NEW)                                     │\n  35→│                    src/services/telegram-pusher.js                           │\n  36→│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐    │\n  37→│  │ • pushHeartbeat()     • pushErrorSummary()                          │    │\n  38→│  │ • sendMessageChunked() • throttle()                                 │    │\n  39→│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘    │\n  40→└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n  41→                    │                      │\n  42→                    ▼                      ▼\n  43→┌─────────────────────────┐ ┌─────────────────────────┐\n  44→│   State Manager (F-004) │ │  Pipeline Controller    │\n  45→│    state-manager.js     │ │  pipeline-controller.js │\n  46→├─────────────────────────┤ ├─────────────────────────┤\n  47→│ • readDaemonMeta()      │ │ • getStatus()           │\n  48→│ • readPipelineState()   │ │ • getLogs()             │\n  49→│ • getLastResult()       │ │                         │\n  50→└─────────────────────────┘ └─────────────────────────┘\n  51→                    │                      │\n  52→                    └──────────────────────┘\n  53→                                           ▼\n  54→                    ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n  55→                    │                       State Files                       │\n  56→                    │  state/pipeline.json, state/.pipeline-meta.json        │\n  57→                    │  state/pipeline-daemon.log, state/.last-result.json    │\n  58→                    │  bugfix-state/... (mirror structure)                    │\n  59→                    └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n  60→```\n  61→\n  62→---\n  63→\n  64→## 2. Component Design\n  65→\n  66→### 2.1 Status Aggregator (`src/services/status-aggregator.js`)\n  67→\n  68→**职责**: 聚合多个状态源，生成结构化的状态报告\n  69→\n  70→**核心方法**:\n  71→\n  72→```javascript\n  73→export function createStatusAggregator(options = {}) {\n  74→  const {\n  75→    stateManager = getDefaultStateManager(),\n  76→    pipelineController = getDefaultPipelineController(),\n  77→    config = loadPipelineInfraConfig()\n  78→  } = options;\n  79→\n  80→  return {\n  81→    // Main aggregation\n  82→    async aggregateStatus(type),\n  83→\n  84→    // Formatting\n  85→    formatStatusForTelegram(status),\n  86→\n  87→    // Helpers\n  88→    calculateProgress(state),\n  89→    getErrorSummary(lastResult),\n  90→    determinePipelineStage(state, daemonMeta),\n  91→  };\n  92→}\n  93→```\n  94→\n  95→**状态聚合流程**:\n  96→1. 读取 `pipeline.json` 获取运行状态\n  97→2. 读取 `.pipeline-meta.json` 获取 daemon 信息\n  98→3. 读取 `.last-result.json` 获取历史结果\n  99→4. 读取 `current-session.json` 获取当前 feature\n 100→5. 聚合生成统一的状态对象\n 101→\n 102→---\n 103→\n 104→### 2.2 Log Pager (`src/services/log-pager.js`)\n 105→\n 106→**职责**: 分页读取日志，支持偏移和行数限制\n 107→\n 108→**核心方法**:\n 109→\n 110→```javascript\n 111→export function createLogPager(options = {}) {\n 112→  const {\n 113→    stateManager = getDefaultStateManager(),\n 114→    config = loadPipelineInfraConfig()\n 115→  } = options;\n 116→\n 117→  return {\n 118→    // Main reading\n 119→    async readLogPage(type, options),\n 120→\n 121→    // Formatting\n 122→    formatLogsForTelegram(logs, metadata),\n 123→\n 124→    // Helpers\n 125→    extractErrorLines(logs, lineCount),\n 126→    shouldSendAsFile(logs, thresholdBytes),\n 127→    buildLogMetadata(logPath, totalLines, pageStart, pageEnd),\n 128→  };\n 129→}\n 130→```\n 131→\n 132→**日志读取流程**:\n 133→1. 解析分页参数 (lines, offset)\n 134→2. 读取日志文件（流式读取大文件）\n 135→3. 提取指定范围\n 136→4. 生成格式化输出\n 137→\n 138→---\n 139→\n 140→### 2.3 Telegram Pusher (`src/services/telegram-pusher.js`)\n 141→\n 142→**职责**: 管理 Telegram 消息推送，包括心跳和错误摘要\n 143→\n 144→**核心方法**:\n 145→\n 146→```javascript\n 147→export function createTelegramPusher(options = {}) {\n 148→  const {\n 149→    bot,\n 150→    targetChatId,\n 151→    heartbeatFeatureCount = 1, // N features completed before push check\n 152→    errorLinesCount = 10,\n 153→    throttleInterval = 30 * 1000, // minimum 30s between pushes\n 154→    maxRetries = 3,\n 155→    retryBaseDelay = 1000, // exponential backoff base\n 156→  } = options;\n 157→\n 158→  return {\n 159→    // Heartbeat (event-based with throttle)\n 160→    onFeatureCompleted(type, featureId, aggregator), // called by lifecycle hook\n 161→    pushProgressUpdate(type, aggregator), // throttled push\n 162→    startHeartbeat(type, aggregator), // register hooks\n 163→    stopHeartbeat(type), // cleanup\n 164→\n 165→    // Error push (via queue)\n 166→    async pushErrorSummary(type, featureId, error),\n 167→\n 168→    // Queue management\n 169→    enqueueMessage(message), // add to in-memory queue\n 170→    processQueue(), // background processor with retry\n 171→\n 172→    // Message sending\n 173→    async sendMessageChunked(chatId, text),\n 174→    async sendFile(chatId, content, filename),\n 175→\n 176→    // Throttling\n 177→    throttle(key, fn),\n 178→  };\n 179→}\n 180→```\n 181→\n 182→**推送流程**:\n 183→1. Pipeline 启动时调用 `startHeartbeat`，注册生命周期事件监听\n 184→2. Pipeline 触发 `onFeatureCompleted` 回调时，检查是否满足推送条件\n 185→3. 通过 `throttle()` 确保推送间隔 ≥ 30 秒，避免刷屏\n 186→4. 消息进入内存队列，后台处理器异步发送（含重试）\n 187→5. Pipeline 停止时调用 `stopHeartbeat`，清理监听器\n 188→\n 189→---\n 190→\n 191→### 2.4 Enhanced Status Handler (`src/bot/commands/handlers/status.js`)\n 192→\n 193→**增强现有处理器**:\n 194→\n 195→```javascript\n 196→export async function handleStatus(handlerCtx) {\n 197→  const { reply, params } = handlerCtx;\n 198→  const pipelineType = params.type || 'feature';\n 199→\n 200→  const aggregator = createStatusAggregator();\n 201→  const status = await aggregator.aggregateStatus(pipelineType);\n 202→  const formatted = aggregator.formatStatusForTelegram(status);\n 203→\n 204→  await reply(formatted);\n 205→}\n 206→```\n 207→\n 208→---\n 209→\n 210→### 2.5 Enhanced Logs Handler (`src/bot/commands/handlers/logs.js`)\n 211→\n 212→**增强现有处理器**:\n 213→\n 214→```javascript\n 215→export async function handleLogs(handlerCtx) {\n 216→  const { reply, replyFile, params } = handlerCtx;\n 217→\n 218→  const pager = createLogPager();\n 219→  const result = await pager.readLogPage(params.type || 'feature', {\n 220→    lines: parseInt(params.lines) || 50,\n 221→    offset: parseInt(params.offset) || 0\n 222→  });\n 223→\n 224→  if (params.file || pager.shouldSendAsFile(result.logs)) {\n 225→    await replyFile(result.logs, `pipeline-logs-${Date.now()}.txt`);\n 226→  } else {\n 227→    const formatted = pager.formatLogsForTelegram(result.logs, result.metadata);\n 228→    await sendChunked(reply, formatted);\n 229→  }\n 230→}\n 231→```\n 232→\n 233→---\n 234→\n 235→## 3. Interface Design\n 236→\n 237→### 3.1 Status Aggregator API\n 238→\n 239→#### `aggregateStatus(type)`\n 240→\n 241→**Input**:\n 242→```typescript\n 243→type PipelineType = 'feature' | 'bugfix';\n 244→```\n 245→\n 246→**Output**:\n 247→```typescript\n 248→interface AggregatedStatus {\n 249→  // Basic info\n 250→  stage: 'running' | 'paused' | 'completed' | 'failed' | 'idle';\n 251→  type: PipelineType;\n 252→  timestamp: string;\n 253→\n 254→  // Progress\n 255→  progress: {\n 256→    total: number;\n 257→    completed: number;\n 258→    failed: number;\n 259→    inProgress: number;\n 260→    successRate: number; // percentage\n 261→  };\n 262→\n 263→  // Current execution\n 264→  current?: {\n 265→    featureId: string;\n 266→    startedAt: string;\n 267→    duration: number; // seconds\n 268→  };\n 269→\n 270→  // Last result\n 271→  lastResult?: {\n 272→    runId: string;\n 273→    completedAt: string;\n 274→    status: 'success' | 'failed' | 'partial';\n 275→    summary: string;\n 276→  };\n 277→\n 278→  // Daemon info\n 279→  daemon?: {\n 280→    pid: number;\n 281→    startedAt: string;\n 282→    uptime: number; // seconds\n 283→  };\n 284→\n 285→  // Error summary (if failed)\n 286→  errors?: Array<{\n 287→    featureId: string;\n 288→    errorType: string;\n 289→    message: string;\n 290→  }>;\n 291→}\n 292→```\n 293→\n 294→---\n 295→\n 296→### 3.2 Log Pager API\n 297→\n 298→#### `readLogPage(type, options)`\n 299→\n 300→**Input**:\n 301→```typescript\n 302→interface LogPageOptions {\n 303→  lines?: number;      // Default: 50, Max: 500\n 304→  offset?: number;     // Default: 0\n 305→  reverse?: boolean;   // Default: true (newest first)\n 306→}\n 307→```\n 308→\n 309→**Output**:\n 310→```typescript\n 311→interface LogPageResult {\n 312→  ok: boolean;\n 313→  logs: string;\n 314→  metadata: {\n 315→    logPath: string;\n 316→    totalLines: number;\n 317→    pageStart: number;\n 318→    pageEnd: number;\n 319→    requestedLines: number;\n 320→    actualLines: number;\n 321→  };\n 322→  errorCode?: string;\n 323→  message?: string;\n 324→}\n 325→```\n 326→\n 327→---\n 328→\n 329→### 3.3 Telegram Pusher API\n 330→\n 331→#### `pushErrorSummary(type, featureId, error)`\n 332→\n 333→**Input**:\n 334→```typescript\n 335→interface ErrorSummaryInput {\n 336→  type: PipelineType;\n 337→  featureId: string;\n 338→  error: {\n 339→    type: string;\n 340→    message: string;\n 341→    stack?: string;\n 342→    logLines?: string[];\n 343→  };\n 344→}\n 345→```\n 346→\n 347→**Output**:\n 348→```typescript\n 349→interface PushResult {\n 350→  ok: boolean;\n 351→  messageId?: string;\n 352→  errorCode?: string;\n 353→}\n 354→```\n 355→\n 356→#### `enqueueMessage(message)`\n 357→\n 358→**Input**:\n 359→```typescript\n 360→interface QueuedMessage {\n 361→  id: string;\n 362→  chatId: number;\n 363→  text: string;\n 364→  type: 'heartbeat' | 'error' | 'notification';\n 365→  priority: number; // lower = higher priority\n 366→  createdAt: number;\n 367→  retryCount: number;\n 368→}\n 369→```\n 370→\n 371→**Retry Logic**:\n 372→- Max retries: 3\n 373→- Backoff: exponential (1s → 2s → 4s)\n 374→- On final failure: log error, discard message (no blocking)\n 375→\n 376→---\n 377→\n 378→## 4. Data Model\n 379→\n 380→### 4.1 Aggregated Status Schema\n 381→\n 382→**Internal representation**:\n 383→\n 384→```json\n 385→{\n 386→  \"stage\": \"running\",\n 387→  \"type\": \"feature\",\n 388→  \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T10:30:00Z\",\n 389→  \"progress\": {\n 390→    \"total\": 10,\n 391→    \"completed\": 4,\n 392→    \"failed\": 1,\n 393→    \"inProgress\": 1,\n 394→    \"successRate\": 80.0\n 395→  },\n 396→  \"current\": {\n 397→    \"featureId\": \"F-005\",\n 398→    \"startedAt\": \"2026-03-13T10:25:00Z\",\n 399→    \"duration\": 300\n 400→  },\n 401→  \"daemon\": {\n 402→    \"pid\": 12345,\n 403→    \"startedAt\": \"2026-03-13T10:00:00Z\",\n 404→    \"uptime\": 1800\n 405→  }\n 406→}\n 407→```\n 408→\n 409→### 4.2 Log Metadata Schema\n 410→\n 411→```json\n 412→{\n 413→  \"logPath\": \"/path/to/pipeline-daemon.log\",\n 414→  \"totalLines\": 1500,\n 415→  \"pageStart\": 1450,\n 416→  \"pageEnd\": 1500,\n 417→  \"requestedLines\": 50,\n 418→  \"actualLines\": 50\n 419→}\n 420→```\n 421→\n 422→### 4.3 Heartbeat Config Schema\n 423→\n 424→**Path**: `{stateDir}/.heartbeat-config.json` (optional)\n 425→\n 426→```json\n 427→{\n 428→  \"enabled\": true,\n 429→  \"intervalMs\": 30000,\n 430→  \"chatId\": 123456789,\n 431→  \"silentMode\": false,\n 432→  \"errorLinesCount\": 10\n 433→}\n 434→```\n 435→\n 436→---\n 437→\n 438→## 5. Module Dependencies\n 439→\n 440→```\n 441→status-aggregator.js\n 442→    ├── state-manager.js (F-004)\n 443→    ├── pipeline-controller.js (F-004)\n 444→    └── config-loader.js (existing)\n 445→\n 446→log-pager.js\n 447→    ├── state-manager.js (F-004)\n 448→    └── config-loader.js (existing)\n 449→\n 450→telegram-pusher.js\n 451→    ├── status-aggregator.js (NEW)\n 452→    ├── log-pager.js (NEW)\n 453→    └── Telegraf bot instance (existing)\n 454→\n 455→status.js (handler)\n 456→    └── status-aggregator.js (NEW)\n 457→\n 458→logs.js (handler)\n 459→    └── log-pager.js (NEW)\n 460→```\n 461→\n 462→---\n 463→\n 464→## 6. Testing Strategy\n 465→\n 466→### 6.1 Unit Tests\n 467→\n 468→| Module | Test File | Focus |\n 469→|--------|-----------|-------|\n 470→| status-aggregator.js | `tests/services/status-aggregator.test.js` | Aggregation logic, progress calculation, formatting |\n 471→| log-pager.js | `tests/services/log-pager.test.js` | Pagination, error extraction, file threshold |\n 472→| telegram-pusher.js | `tests/services/telegram-pusher.test.js` | Throttling, chunking, heartbeat timing |\n 473→\n 474→### 6.2 Integration Tests\n 475→\n 476→**File**: `tests/integration/f005-status-and-logs.integration.test.js`\n 477→\n 478→| Test Case | Description |\n 479→|-----------|-------------|\n 480→| Full Status Flow | Query status for running/idle pipeline |\n 481→| Log Pagination | Read logs with offset/lines parameters |\n 482→| Message Chunking | Verify long messages split correctly |\n 483→| Heartbeat Push | Verify heartbeat triggers and throttles |\n 484→| Error Summary Push | Verify error summary format |\n 485→| Diagnostic Errors | Verify error messages for missing files |\n 486→\n 487→### 6.3 Test Coverage Target\n 488→\n 489→- Core modules: > 85% branch coverage\n 490→- Integration tests: All user stories covered\n 491→\n 492→---\n 493→\n 494→## 7. Risk Assessment\n 495→\n 496→| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation | Owner |\n 497→|------|-------------|--------|------------|-------|\n 498→| Telegram API rate limiting | Medium | Medium | Throttle messages, batch with intervals | Dev |\n 499→| State file race condition | Low | Medium | Read with tolerance for stale data | Dev |\n 500→| Large log file memory | Low | Medium | Stream read with line limit | Dev |\n 501→| Push failure blocking | Low | High | Async queue, fire-and-forget | Dev |\n 502→| Message formatting issues | Low | Low | Template-based formatting, escape special chars | Dev |\n 503→\n 504→---\n 505→\n 506→## 8. User Story to Component Mapping\n 507→\n 508→| User Story | Primary Component | Supporting Components |\n 509→|------------|-------------------|----------------------|\n 510→| US-1: Aggregated Status Query | status-aggregator.js | status.js handler |\n 511→| US-2: Paginated Logs Query | log-pager.js | logs.js handler |\n 512→| US-3: Message Length Compliance | log-pager.js (chunking) | telegram-pusher.js |\n 513→| US-4: Heartbeat Progress Push | telegram-pusher.js | status-aggregator.js |\n 514→| US-5: Error Summary Push | telegram-pusher.js | log-pager.js |\n 515→| US-6: Diagnostic Error Messages | status-aggregator.js, log-pager.js | error-codes.js |\n 516→\n 517→---\n 518→\n 519→## 9. Implementation Phases\n 520→\n 521→### Phase 1: Foundation (T-001 ~ T-009)\n 522→- Setup test infrastructure\n 523→- Create service modules skeleton\n 524→- Define interfaces\n 525→\n 526→### Phase 2: Core Services (T-010 ~ T-099)\n 527→- Implement status-aggregator.js\n 528→- Implement log-pager.js\n 529→- Implement telegram-pusher.js\n 530→\n 531→### Phase 3: User Story Implementation (T-100+)\n 532→- US-1: Aggregated Status Query\n 533→- US-2: Paginated Logs Query\n 534→- US-3: Message Length Compliance\n 535→- US-4: Heartbeat Progress Push\n 536→- US-5: Error Summary Push\n 537→- US-6: Diagnostic Error Messages\n 538→\n 539→### Phase 4: Integration & Polish (T-900+)\n 540→- Integration tests\n 541→- Documentation updates\n 542→- Edge case handling\n 543→\n 544→---\n 545→\n 546→## 10. Key Decisions\n 547→\n 548→| ID | Decision | Rationale |\n 549→|----|----------|-----------|\n 550→| D1 | 独立状态聚合服务 | 保持 pipeline-controller 单一职责，便于测试和扩展 |\n 551→| D2 | 内存消息队列 + 重试 | 推送失败不阻塞主流程，重试确保可靠性 |\n 552→| D3 | 命令行参数分页 | 简化实现，避免复杂分页协议 |\n 553→| D4 | 事件驱动心跳 + 时间节流 | 按 feature 完成触发，节流避免刷屏 |\n 554→| D5 | 实时日志错误提取 | 不额外存储错误信息，减少状态管理复杂度 |\n 555→| D6 | 复用现有消息分段机制 | telegram.js 已有 splitMessage，避免重复实现 |\n 556→| D7 | 最小化生命周期钩子 | 仅在 pipeline-controller 添加 onPipelineStart/onPipelineStop 钩子，不修改核心执行逻辑 |\n 557→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_475ad05a155d4431bd73ba2b","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:22:20.665Z","_requestId":"2a50dd388a364b15840cdcad9dcd8a24"}
{"type":"user","uuid":"3c3ca1aa-642f-4923-bc3e-3a3e9bd0fa61","session_id":"da6f98d4-7e33-4c58-9c42-a371874e10ea","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde908890aba8f9073d1305fbec92","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1→# F-005: Pipeline Status Aggregation and Log Streaming — Task Breakdown\n   2→\n   3→## Phase 1: Setup (T-001 ~ T-009)\n   4→\n   5→- [x] [T-001] [P] Create test file skeleton for status-aggregator — file: tests/services/status-aggregator.test.js\n   6→- [x] [T-002] [P] Create test file skeleton for log-pager — file: tests/services/log-pager.test.js\n   7→- [x] [T-003] [P] Create test file skeleton for telegram-pusher — file: tests/services/telegram-pusher.test.js\n   8→- [x] [T-004] Create status-aggregator.js module skeleton with interface types — file: src/services/status-aggregator.js\n   9→- [x] [T-005] Create log-pager.js module skeleton with interface types — file: src/services/log-pager.js\n  10→- [x] [T-006] Create telegram-pusher.js module skeleton with interface types — file: src/services/telegram-pusher.js\n  11→- [x] [T-007] [P] Add error codes for status/log operations to error-codes.js — file: src/pipeline-infra/error-codes.js\n  12→- [x] [T-008] Create integration test skeleton for F-005 — file: tests/integration/f005-status-and-logs.integration.test.js\n  13→- [x] [T-009] Export new services from index — file: src/services/index.js\n  14→\n  15→---\n  16→\n  17→## Phase 2: Foundational (T-010 ~ T-099)\n  18→\n  19→### Status Aggregator Core\n  20→\n  21→- [x] [T-010] Implement aggregateStatus() to read all state sources — file: src/services/status-aggregator.js\n  22→- [x] [T-011] Implement determinePipelineStage() to classify pipeline state — file: src/services/status-aggregator.js\n  23→- [x] [T-012] Implement calculateProgress() for completed/failed/inProgress stats — file: src/services/status-aggregator.js\n  24→- [x] [T-013] Implement getErrorSummary() to extract errors from lastResult — file: src/servic